Revoke permissions
==================

desktop:
MariaDB [iant]> revoke select on iant.iant_users from u3;
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.00 sec)

MariaDB [iant]>

server:
MariaDB [iant]> show tables;
ERROR 1044 (42000): Access denied for user 'u3'@'%' to database 'iant'
